I"Ó<ul>
  <li>Name : ER_OLEDM1_CH1115_RPI</li>
  <li>
    <p>Title : Library to support the ER-OLEDM1.09-1 128X64 OLED Display Module driven by the CH1115 controller for the Raspberry Pi  eco-system.</p>
  </li>
  <li>Description :</li>
</ul>

<ol>
  <li>Raspberry Pi library C++.</li>
  <li>Inverse colour, vertical rotate, sleep, fade effect, horizontal scroll and contrast control.</li>
  <li>Extended ASCII scalable font.</li>
  <li>Graphics class included.</li>
  <li>3 different modes: Multi-buffer , single buffer , no buffer.</li>
  <li>Bitmaps supported.</li>
  <li>Hardware &amp; software SPI options</li>
  <li>Tested on Raspberry PI 3 model b, C++ ,Raspbian 9.13 stretch</li>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/gavinlyonsrepo/ER_OLEDM1_CH1115">Port</a> of my arduino Library for ER-OLEDM1.09-1  , CH1115 controller,</li>
</ol>

<ul>
  <li>Author: Gavin Lyons</li>
</ul>

